item.title: [On-going project] Epiformer: Transformer based deep learning architecture for Epigenetic features prediction
item.description: Aim The project aims to optimize the architecture of Enformer for predicting epigenetic features by redesigning the building blocks of deep learning architecture specifically for DNA sequence processing and incorporating neural architecture search techniques, resulting in significant improvements.
